Developed a basic version of an e-commerce platform resembling Amazon or Flipkart, focusing on creating a user-friendly interface and implementing essential back-end logic for user interactions.
Designed and implemented an intuitive user interface for the e-commerce platform, featuring a visually appealing logo, a functional search bar, and seamless navigation for account management, returns, orders, and categorized product listings. Employed user-centric design principles to enhance overall user experience.
Engineered robust back-end logic for the e-commerce platform, incorporating functionalities like user authentication, order processing, and data storage. Utilized Java, JavaFX and MySQL to ensure seamless communication between the user interface and the underlying database, contributing to a smooth and responsive user experience.
